Quickstrike:




Quickstrike nodded to Paralysis and went. It came to a surprised to him that 
he was being called sir. He was the one who usually called others sir. It 
was mainly Megatron he called that. When he was in trouble. He usually 
called him boss.

He looked around the dark area. His crimson optics glowed brightly on face. 
He came to Aerostreak. He looked at him and looked at the ground. "This 
where th' bunker is?"
